@CALLOWED FIELDS@n   : Trigger, Value, Command, Target, String.

@CDESCRIPTION@n:

Typing @caset <trigger>@n will list the various @ctrigger options@n for
actions.  @CNOTE@n: You must be editing an acode for this to work.

The @ccommand@n field specifies what command typed by a player in the
room will trigger the action.  The field can have multiple one-word
entries separtated by a space.

