0 0 19 Dal'Entil Village~
.Recently, an upheaval in the stability of the Cairn Mountains caused a
minor avalanche.  When the dust and rubble cleared, a crevice was opened
through the cliff face that lies in the far north beyond Kha-da.  Those
sent to investigate, report that the crevice is passable and opens onto a
wilderness trail leading beyond the mountain's heights.  No one has, as
yet, investigated what lies at the other end of the trail, but ancient
legends speak of a valley hidden deep with the Cairns away from mortal
ken.
~

