0 0 10 Half-Elves~
.@GAverage Statistics for Half-Elves@n

Height: males about 4'8"-5'10'
        females about 4'6"-5'8"

Hair: Ranging in colors usally tending towards lighter colors, but a few with
      black hair have been seen. Half-elves also tend to have little to no
      facial hair

Eyes: Primarily Blue, Green or (rarely) Gray iris. A few Half-Elves also have
      the almond shaped eyes of the elves.

Affiliation: light or dark based on alignment / how you role-play it.

Appearance: Half-elves always appear more human than elven or vyan.  Though
neither as tall nor as muscular as humans, half-elves have sturdy frames.
Their hair, skin and eyes comes in a variety of different shades, depending
upon the dominant features of their parents.  A half-elf has slightly
less pronounced pointed ears but can manage a full beard, unlike those of
elven blood.  The skin tones of most half-elves is a slightly golden color,
though this can vary depending upon their human blood.

@GOptional Advice on Role Playing an Half-Elf@n

Half-Elves are as the name implies the offspring of a human and an elf or vyan.
As such they are shunned by all most all other races. They are nomadic in
nature rarely staying in one town long. Many Half-Elves have been killed by
other races who fear them saying they are an abomination as mixed breeds. 
Those who make it past adolsence have had to learned to be independant,
trusting no one in order to survive.
~

