Prefix_P    : Posts before Plural, and before Adj_P.  Optional.
              A descriptive field for the very beginning of a mob's appearance.
Adj_P       : Posts after Prefix_P, but before Plural.  Optional.
              A descriptive field for the beginning of a mob's appearance
Long_P      : Posts after Plural field.   Required.
              A descriptive field for the end of a mob's appearance.  Usually
