.Monks are extremely deadly fighters specializing in unarmed combat.  As
@CLegacy's Dawning@n is not set in an Asian-type setting, monks are not
necessarily analogous to 'traditional' monks, but instead represent
experts at individual, unarmed combat.  Included in their plethora of
physical abilities are the skills of @Ctiger paw@n, @Cdragon strike@n,
and @Ccritical hit@n, which multiply the damage done on a strike.  Higher
level monks attain the abilities of @Cdeath strike@n, and @Cdemon slash@n. 
