16 0 27 Mreset_Repop_Guide~
.@CMreset Repop Guide@n

Following, please find suggested mreset chances for most mundane armors.

Bronze mundane armor: (mob level/5)%. Shouldn't pop on mob under level 10.
Iron mundane armor: (mob level/10)%. Shouldn't pop on mob under level 25.
Steel mundane armor: (mob level/15)%. Shouldn't pop on mob under level 40.
Mithril mundane armor: (mob level/20)%. Shouldn't pop on mob under level 55.

Mundane weapons: see armor of same material.  Double reset chances and
halve the level they shouldn't appear on.

Magic items: (mob level/5) - (item level/5) = mreset%.  Mobs can't pop an
item higher level than they are.  If they pop an item the same level as
they are, reset should be set to 1%.

The most important fact to remember is that you are NOT setting the
percent chance that an item is ON the mob, you are setting the chance
that is it on the mob, and survived the combat well enough to be useful
to a player.~

