0 0 21 Strongholds~
.                 @yThe Dwarven Labor Union@n
      @yPrice List for the Building of Clan Strongholds@n

@C*  @nThe basic clan stronghold consists of three rooms and your clan
insignia.  Flat rate for this is @G350k@c.

@C* @nA basic locked door and key comes complimentary with your clan
house.  However for those of you who would like a little more secrecy,
you can add a hidden entrance to your clan house.  The price of this
added feature will be between @G15k@n and @G50k@n depending on how
elaborate you want to get.  Additional locked, non-secret doors are
priced at @G15K@n.

@C* @nExtra rooms leading up to a Stronghold will be priced at @G25k@n
for the first two rooms, then @G50k@n for each room after that.

@C* @nSecret rooms will not be part of the basic three rooms.  To create
a secret room, you will be charged @G100k@n for an extra room as well as
an additional @G50k@n for the concealment of the door and hidden lever.

@C* @nStorage rooms and banks are inclusive and are available for your
stronghold at the cost of @G100k@n for the flag, with an additional
purchase cost of @G100k@n for the room itself.  These rooms save over
crashes/reboots, and do not reset.  Items will stay indefinitely either
on the ground or in chests, should you choose to purchase them.  Large,
300 pound capacity chests are priced at @G3.5k@n and 1000 pound capacity
chests are priced at @G10k@n each.

@C*  @nAdding arenas to your stronghold is also possible, at a cost of
@G100k@n for the extra room plus 100k for the arena flag.

@C*  @nExtras in the room, such as pictures on the wall you can look at,
will cost you @G10k@n per description.

@C*  @nWhen you're relaxing in your new Stronghold or having an important
meeting, you may want to have a few tables, chairs or couches for you and
your guests.  The price for a basic piece of furniture will be @G5k@n,
but if you want some exotic custom item, it's going to be charged at a
custom price.  (Such as a throne or a dragon leather couch.) 

@C* @nFor those of you who would like a fountain built in your
Stronghold, the charge is @G50k@n for materials and labour.  Soup
cauldrons will also cost @G75k@n for stocking and labour.  Note that
there will be no fountains containing any special liquids, such as youth
potion, taengle wine, as it is beyond the skill of the dwarven laborers.

@C*  @nActions, such as 'You smell a delicious aroma waft up from the
kettle of soup,' will cost @G25k@n per action.  Note that elaborate
actions may cost up to four times the normal rate, dependant on their
complexity.

@C* @nExtra-Planer placement, The charge for this is high as it takes an
extreme amount of arcane energy to accomplish the task.  The cost is
@G500k@n for a new stronghold to be placed on its own plane and @G750k@n
for an existing stronghold to be 'transported'.  @RThis is not available
at this time@n.

If there is something you would like for your clan house that is not
listed here, please ask about it and it can be submitted to the Union for
consideration.  However, Dwarves being the practical creatures they are,
please try to keep your requests within the bounds of reality.

See also: stronghold_rules
