Entanglement spells softcode balance formula is currently as follows:
Hitpoints = (spell_level+L)*((mob_stand_dice+mob_stand_dice/2)/2)
calc out that mob_stand dice manually and round generously
since the formula doesn't accept decimals
eg web = level 17, so its (17+L)*x
looking at mob standards, a level 17 mob gets d10 hitpoints, so its
(10+10/2)/2 = 7.5 so rounded up to 8 
so (17+L)*8 works
