0 0 8 Who~
.@cSYNTAX@n

@Cwho@n    : lists all visible players on

@cDESCRIPTION@n

The @Cwho@n list will list all players who are visible and online.  Each player
is placed in a category according to how well you know them.  The first
category is self-explanatory: @cImmortal@n.  The @cbefriended@n category will list
all people who are on that are @cbefriended@n to you.  The @cknown@n category lists
people who you are introduced to but not @cbefriended@n.  The @cunknown@n category
lists people who you have not been introduced to.  Each player can only
appear once on the who list, so someone who is @cbefriended@n will not appear
in the @cknown@n category.

