You may notice two letters after a player's information, these may be one of:
[ AV ] Avatar - someone to help you with your description approval
[ CL ] Clan Leader - person responsible for managing a clan
[ LD ] Link Dead - this person has lost link and may not get back to you

See also: @CLast@n, @CWhois@n
