0 0 14 Yell~
.@cSYNTAX@n

yell <string> : sends a string to all rooms in your area

@cDESCRIPTION@n

Use @Cyell@n to send a message to everyone in your present area.  It costs no
gossip points, and can be useful if, for instance, you become separated
from your group in a perilous place (and you like to roleplay).  It is also
of use when communicating with others not in your group, but still nearby.
If you wish to send a string to the entire mud, see the @CShout@n command.

Note that like @CChat@n, @CGossip@n, @CAuction@n, and even @CShout@n, this is a channel in
which profanity is @Cnot@n acceptable.~

