@cDESCRIPTION@n

You use the @Czap@n command to use one of your wands upon a target.  Wands
generally have charges and the use of @Czap@n will expend a charge.  When
depleted of all of their charges, wands make excellent kindling.  You must
be holding a wand in order to be able to @Czap@n with it.
~

